    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely pristine shape\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just left the dealership. I\u2019ve babied it from day one, so you're getting a ride that's been cared for with a ton of love. It\u2019s super clean, runs like a dream, and is ready to hit the road today. Come check it out!",
