    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) is a concourse-quality specimen, showcasing the pinnacle of the water-cooled flat-six evolution. Powered by the 3.6L M96 engine with VarioCam Plus, it delivers linear power delivery across the rev range. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers precise shift gates, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Chassis dynamics are preserved with original-spec Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings, ensuring zero lateral play. The undercarriage is clinically clean, reflecting a life of climate-controlled storage. Recent preventative maintenance includes a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a high-flow water pump. This is a turn-key collector's piece for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
