    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty in person to believe it. I've babied this car since day one, and it truly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. The paint is flawless, the interior is spotless, and everything is in absolutely pristine condition. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, but it's time for a new home. If you're looking for a ride that feels brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you! Drop me a message and come take a look!",
      "price": 44900.0,
