      "description": "Presented in concours-level condition, this 996.2 Carrera 4S features the definitive 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six, delivering linear power through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The integrated dry-sump lubrication and a documented LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit ensure mechanical longevity. This wide-body example retains its factory-spec Viscous Multi-Plate AWD system, providing exceptional lateral grip. The chassis remains taut, riding on a refined multi-link rear suspension with four-piston monoblock Brembo calipers providing fade-free deceleration. Meticulously maintained with zero bore scoring and a pristine undercarriage.",
